sequenceDiagram
  actor User
  participant Planner
  participant Model as AI Model
  participant Tools as Read-only/Web Tools
  participant Selector
  participant Runner as Step Runner
  participant Approval

  User->>Planner: Provide goal
  Planner->>Model: Request structured plan
  Model->>Tools: Research codebase or web
  Tools-->>Model: Observations
  Model-->>Planner: Plan JSON
  Planner->>Selector: Present plan
  User->>Selector: Select steps
  Selector->>Runner: Execute selected steps
  Runner->>Approval: Review staged mutations
